---
title: Speedy Chipotle Chicken Breast Penne with Pepper and Cheese
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, this Speedy Chipotle Chicken Penne has it all. The main flavour here comes from chipotle, full of rich, smoky and fruity flavours with a kick from the chipotle chillies.
